{"tid":2004470,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"真男人頂起來！推特炒熱「頂洗髮精挑戰」，考驗男人GG硬實力！","createTime":"2020-05-06T12:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T13:19:19.000Z","uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d2e8a6499d4a25d63efe52cee8daece5b898950","tid":2004470,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"近期，在Twitter上最火的熱門標籤#ShampooChallenge「老二頂洗髮精挑戰」，這個乍看名字，感覺無色無害，甚至有點不知所云的網路挑戰活動，其實都是從一張漫畫圖燒起...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-manfashion.techbang.com/system/images/111166/medium/e9d3f5be30af716bc3aaa3e66b5268c6.jpg?1588566066\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-manfashion.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F111166%2Fmedium%2Fe9d3f5be30af716bc3aaa3e66b5268c6.jpg%3F1588566066&h=9e6422f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 一切都是從這張看似惡搞的漫畫圖開始「老二頂洗髮精」挑戰... Photo Source<br />\n<br />\n#「老二頂洗髮精挑戰」考驗男人的GG硬實力！<br />\n「ShampooChallenge」原意其實只是洗髮精挑戰，但配上「上圖」示範便能讓你秒懂箇中含義！這個「老二頂洗髮精挑戰」，顧名思義，就是要靠男人喚醒巨龍後，藉由老二長度創造空間，硬度打造支撐力，隔著內褲將GG橫擺，看是否能成功擺放上具有一定重量洗髮精作為挑戰，藉此評斷你的「男人力」是否夠給力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mf.techbang.com/posts/11011-a-real-man-twitter-hype-hot-top-wash-essence-challenge-testing-the-hard-strength-of-men-gg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmf.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F11011-a-real-man-twitter-hype-hot-top-wash-essence-challenge-testing-the-hard-strength-of-men-gg&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=a3883463\" target=\"_blank\">https://mf.techbang.com/posts/11011-a-real-man-twitter-hype-hot-top-wash-essence-challenge-testing-the-hard-strength-of-men-gg</a>"},{"pid":"6dae79e7442c1866f13cf5c2bab82002b3885448","tid":2004470,"uid":210087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8